		&lt;li&gt;Payment of interest, installments of loans, insurance premiums, etc.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Purchase and sale of securities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Collection of interest, dividend, etc&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Transfer of funds through demand drafts, mail transfer, etc&lt;/li&gt;
